# --- 2026-07-20 (per operator request) ---
# Marketing image assets that churn on this machine (external re-encodes).
# docs/marketing/frames/ was untracked from the public repo on 2026-07-21
# (git rm -r --cached): it holds only the source stills for hero.gif -
# regenerated by `npm run capture:marketing` - and is not referenced by the
# README. screenshots/ and social-preview.png stay TRACKED (the README embeds
# them); their ignore lines only stop future re-encode churn from showing in
# `git status`, they do not untrack.
