# --- 2026-07-21: trim the public repo to the shipped extension + its
# public-facing docs. Everything below is dev/build scaffolding or internal
# documentation with no runtime tie to the extension. These paths are also
# untracked with `git rm -r --cached` (files stay on disk); .gitignore alone
# does not remove already-tracked paths from the repo.
#
# KEPT public on purpose: docs/marketing/ (all README images),
# docs/planning/ (in-product "Learn more" link targets), and the two
# README-linked Ask AI docs (mcp-chat-prototype.md, ask-ai-local-providers.md).
# The granular tools/* and docs/* entries above are now subsumed by these.

# Dev/build scaffolding: codegen, dev launchers, discovery probes, QA, git-hooks
/tools/

